<h2 id="module1966" class=" moduletitle">University Guide</h2>
<div id='ctl00_leftContent_ctl02_pnlOuterBody' class=''>

<div id='ctl00_leftContent_ctl02_pnlInnerBody' class='modulecontent'>


<div id='ctl00_leftContent_ctl02_divContent' class=''>
<p>
	The University of Oxford's Department of Chemistry tops the subject ranking for Chemistry in the <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/table/2012/may/22/university-guide-chemistry">Guardian's University Guide 2013</a>. The Guide is based on the things students care most about when they are choosing a course.</p>
<p>
	<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/table/2012/may/22/university-guide-chemistry"><img alt="" src="/Data/Sites/21/images/guardian-logo.jpg" style="width: 180px; height: 32px; " /></a></p>

